            <p>The prototype has been tested on 3 people thorough a Gorilla testing.</p>
            <p><strong>Pain points:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                 <li>We expect picture to zoom.. but user expected to go to details pagedropdown menu and filter (colors, prices)</li>
                 <li>One user would have saved his profile if it didn't include credit card</li>
